    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Here, by using `random.shuffle`, the elements inside the list will get shuffled in their sequence. Hence, the final password will be completely random."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Iy1RlPv2F5HE"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#random.shuffle will not genrate a new list. It will just modify the same list\n",
        "#Therefore, you do not have to create a new list for the shuffled sequence\n",
        "\n",
        "random.shuffle(password_list)\n",
        "\n",
        "final_password = delimiter.join(password_list)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"This is your 'shuffled' password\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"The same password from above with the sequence now changed\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(final_password)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
